<Layout title="How to Sell a House in Ashgrove, Brisbane (2026 Guide)" description="Selling in Ashgrove? What sellers need to know about the school-catchment buyer, what drives value in the inner north-west, and how to get the best result.">

<article style="background:var(--color-surface-0);min-height:100vh;">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div style="background:#e6d9bd;padding:8rem 0 3rem;">
    <div class="max-w-[780px] mx-auto px-8">
